# Invite links must answer 200, not 404 — iMessage/WhatsApp link-preview
# crawlers refuse to render a card for a 404 response, which is why texted
# table links showed no preview (Ellen 2026-07-22). These are REWRITES
# (200), not redirects: the URL bar keeps /join/CODE, so the page's
# pathname-parsing JS still reads the code. Every other unknown path still
# falls through to 404.html with a real 404.
/join/*    /404.html   200
/invite/*  /404.html   200
